{"tid":2219648,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭振華：上調最低工資或影響低收入人士就業","createTime":"2020-09-27T04:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T04:50:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8a85b292755f0bd907b207238daef209b66894ab","tid":2219648,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"工業總會名譽會長、勞工顧問委員會資方委員郭振華表示，若凍結最低工資水平，帶出的信息是經濟不穩、企業信心差，即使調高最低工資水平，對勞動市場幫助不大，企業在經營困境下，或有更大機會要求工作能力較弱的低收入人士放無薪假，希望最低工資委員會要考慮有關情況，建議政府研究推出針對低收入人士的補貼計劃。 <br />\n<br />\n郭振華出席一個電視節目時表示，疫情對零售和飲食業影響最深，希望在安全情況下，重啓本港與大灣區經濟活動，令雙方得益。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2359118&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0ojkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=80f298b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359118</a>"},{"pid":"140fa019270bac0420e6d0aa1d9c9522a4c7d7a0","tid":2219648,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:43:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a472dca55840005548d3d0273e1acf838069067","tid":2219648,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"講到加兩蚊成個行業會玩撚完咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b37884988d23a48ffa536ff9c16ce40050f700","tid":2219648,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ece9928234ee20c9f8e7cec964edd8f066b576","tid":2219648,"uid":232185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議政府研究推出針對低收入人士的補貼計劃</blockquote><br />\n覺得依句先係重點"},{"pid":"efb8430192a35b2985791633e1288a856c5fae1c","tid":2219648,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a472dca55840005548d3d0273e1acf838069067","tid":2219648,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,